      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/180dabbabe0c59c8bcd038948f7ec889521051cd.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=058f25e330f73390444d8f7b2957f877"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/26933b1f2be6373710299718e2e20b61f8bfaad1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=e23ead0b801a3744e73576508c849c92"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;The most frightening and fantastic graphic novels&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Take a walk off the beaten literary path and explore the eerie, frightening worlds of James Tynion IV. Our latest comics bundle offers atmospheric and unique ebooks that will surely spice up your summer reading—dive into acclaimed series like &lt;em&gt;The Nice House on the Lake &lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Something is Killing the Children&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;The Oddly Pedestrian Life of Christopher Chaos&lt;/em&gt;, and more. Don’t be scared—explore the frightening and fantastic worlds of James Tynion IV and help support The BINC Foundation with your purchase!&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a style="color: #ef9741;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Nice House on the Lake Vol. 1 and 2 will be available to redeem in August 2025.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#dcuiultra30-daytrialoffer"&gt;DCUI Monthly Ultra 30-Day Free Trial Offer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#somethingiskillingthechildren_vol1"&gt;Something is Killing the Children Vol. 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bluebookvolume1_1961"&gt;Blue Book Volume 1: 1961&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#departmentoftruth_vol1"&gt;DEPARTMENT OF TRUTH, Vol. 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt24"&gt;Pay $24 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#nicehouseonthelake_vol1"&gt;The Nice House on the Lake Vol. 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#nicehouseonthelake_vol2"&gt;