      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5f75ce5770665ca1c1617a6a97fcdf69703770ec.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=47be28548a3769b396c5c791ac41a6f6"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fc10a29c57a9aa31e3ba3c8837e66ca96c1e902c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=d1f32e0e7e0aa5564d1ba68f7cb3002e"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Blockbuster Assets Built for You. Worldbuild like a Pro!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Urban Life Collection bundle of interiors, props and vehicles by KitBash3D puts 500+ blockbuster-quality assets at your fingertips! These studio-grade, fully customizable assets have been used in major films including Dr. Strange, and Spider-Man, popular like The Last of Us, Star Trek: Discovery, and Halo and AAA gaming titles such as The Last of Us Part II, NBA 2K, and The Elder Scrolls, and now they’re available to creators of all levels. Whether you're a hobbyist, beginner or pro, these Kits are built to fit right into your workflow. Fully compatible with Blender, Unreal, Maya, Unity, Houdini, Cinema 4D, 3ds Max, and more, this bundle delivers unmatched value for anyone building cinematic urban scenes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sedan"&gt;Sedan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#citybus"&gt;City Bus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sportscar"&gt;Sports Car&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#boxtruck"&gt;Box Truck&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#apartmentinteriors"&gt;Apartment Interiors&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#retailstores"&gt;Retail Stores&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#policedepartment"&gt;Police Department&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mid-sizesuv"&gt;Mid-Size SUV&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#stationwagon"&gt;Station Wagon&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#compactcitycar"&gt;Compact City Car&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#deliverytruck"&gt;Delivery Truck&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#armoredtruck"&gt;Armored Truck&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#taxicab"&gt;Taxicab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#schoolbus"&gt;School Bus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#policecruiser"&gt;Police Cruiser&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#dumptruck"&gt;Dump Truck&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#loader"&gt;Loader&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#forklift"&gt;Forklift&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="sedan"&gt;&lt;a id="sedan" href="https://youtu.be/ZEJELfe9hZg"&gt;Sedan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;From rush-hour traffic to late-night getaways, this versatile Sedan standing at 1 meter in scale, is a true city essential, equipped with a full interior with 16 meshes and 24 PBR materials.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Its sleek yet practical design makes it the perfect background vehicle, a dynamic element in a high-speed chase, or the personal ride of your story’s lead character. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether it's parked, cruising, or crashing through the scene—this car is ready to drive your narrative forward for any film, games and immersive projects. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 1 Meter in Scale / High Quality Vehicle &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 24 PBR Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unique Handcrafted Vehicle&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Highly Detailed / AAA Quality &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Compatible with Windows, Mac and All Major Software &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 1K, 2K and 4K &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Software:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unreal Engine (5.0 – 5.6)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Blender (Eevee, Cycles)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unity (URP &amp;amp; HDRP)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Houdini (Mantra, Karma)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Cinema 4D &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Autodesk Maya, 3ds Max&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Octane, Redshift, V-Ray, Arnold&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="citybus"&gt;&lt;a id="citybus" href="https://youtu.be/Lp8A-G6TwZU"&gt;City Bus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Navigate the heart of the city with this realistic City Bus. This transportation vehicle stands at 3 meters in scale and is equipped with a detailed interior, 29 meshes, and 25 PBR materials all designed for crowded streets, busy transit hubs, and everyday movement.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With detailed interiors and authentic design elements, this 3D model is perfect for morning commutes, traffic-packed scenes, or setting the rhythm of a vibrant urban environment. Add motion and realism to your world, one stop at a time.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether it's weaving through traffic, or daily commutes this City Bus is perfect for films, games and visualization projects. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 3 Meters In Scale / High Quality Vehicle &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 25 PBR Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 29 Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unique Handcrafted Vehicle&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Highly Detailed / AAA Quality &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Compatible with Windows, Mac and All Major Software &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 1K, 2K and 4K &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Software:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unreal Engine (5.0 – 5.5)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Blender (Eevee, Cycles)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unity (URP &amp;amp; HDRP)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Houdini (Mantra, Karma)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Cinema 4D &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Autodesk Maya, 3ds Max&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Octane, Redshift, V-Ray, Arnold&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="sportscar"&gt;&lt;a id="sportscar" href="https://youtu.be/zJmxgHcBxJI"&gt;Sports Car&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Sports Car is designed for speed and style! Featuring a complete detailed interior, 13 meshes, 27 PBR materials and standing at 1 meter in scale, this sports car delivers high-end performance and cinematic flair for games, films, and visualization.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Its aerodynamic shape, low profile, and bold presence make it the perfect choice for high-speed pursuits, street races, or luxury lifestyle scenes. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether tearing through a neon city or parked outside a penthouse, this car demands attention.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 1 Meter In Scale / High Quality Vehicle &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 27 PBR Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 13 Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unique Handcrafted Vehicle&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Highly Detailed / AAA Quality &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Compatible with Windows, Mac and All Major Software &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 1K, 2K and 4K &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Software:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unreal Engine (5.0 – 5.6)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Blender (Eevee, Cycles)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unity (URP &amp;amp; HDRP)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Houdini (Mantra, Karma)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Cinema 4D &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Autodesk Maya, 3ds Max&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Octane, Redshift, V-Ray, Arnold&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="boxtruck"&gt;&lt;a id="boxtruck" href="https://youtu.be/YfZnOt9QcH8"&gt;Box Truck&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This Box Truck, with a highly detailed interior, 27 meshes, 24 PBR materials and standing at 4 meters in scale, brings logistical realism and functional detail to modern urban scenes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;From warehouse runs to city deliveries this high quality vehicle features a large cargo bay, exterior bra