t;Returning with Volume 3 of the Spy Music Pack by Ovani Sound, this stealthy selection brings suave melodies and mysterious motifs perfect for sneaky missions, espionage themes, and secret agent action.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;A total of 50 music files!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;With each individual track, you’ll find three different intensity levels, each lasting approximately 90 seconds, along with a 30-second rough cut and a 60-second rough cut. Five different variants per track! With 10 distinct tracks, this diverse selection ensures seamless integration into your projects, providing the perfect musical backdrop.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Furthermore, our tracks offer even more value by seamlessly looping when used with our Music Integration Plugins, providing you with enhanced flexibility for your game development process.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;48khz/24bit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mutatedbeingssoundfxpack_vol2"&gt;&lt;a id="mutatedbeingssoundfxpack_vol2" href="https://youtu.be/xLT0VRJzXeQ"&gt;Mutated Beings Sound FX Pack Vol. 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4cc569b51e38e6d1506777fac4ca48585c8f894a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a18e3a85234bfbd5816be7aecde0a29b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Returning with Volume 2 of the Mutated Beings Sound FX Pack by Ovani Sound – a grotesque evolution of the original, loaded with entirely new monstrosities and audio horrors to fuel your nightmares.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With 238 total sounds, this collection unleashes deeply unsettling creature audio designed for horror, sci-fi, survival, and post-apocalyptic settings.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 21 Clacker Sounds – Bone-clicking snarls, labored breaths, and death gurgles.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 24 Exhaler Sounds – Wet gasps, raspy groans, and spine-tingling idle chatter.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 20 Frogger Sounds – Amphibious croaks, guttural death cries, and effortful lunges.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 24 Growler Sounds – Ferocious bellows and dense growls that shake the ground.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 24 Gruffler Sounds – Grunts and guttural vocalizations from grotesque, heavy-set creatures.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 28 Inhaler Sounds – Choking gasps, wheezing attacks, and breath-driven pain cues.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 20 Misc Sounds – Clickers, garglers, rattlers, and unplaceable horrors.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 23 Squealer Sounds – High-pitched, frantic cries from nightmare-fueled entities.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 24 Wheezer Sounds – Labored exhales and panicked gasps with grim urgency.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 30 Worbler Sounds – Distorted attacks, squelching deaths, and pained howls from malformed abominations.&lt;p&gt;Every sound in this pack is brand new and exclusive to Volume 2 – no recycled material. Each monster was carefully designed with layers of texture to add realism and weight to your mutants, aliens, and otherworldly threats.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file is tagged with detailed metadata for fast implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="foley_handgunssoundfxpack"&gt;&lt;a id="foley_handgunssoundfxpack" href="https://youtu.be/rsYk6pKAQoU"&gt;Foley: Handguns Sound FX Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/db49c7e354031e496eab0f6cf3bd0e15396f0565.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=63ba54a7f3fe415c4256116e24bfd9ad"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing the Foley: Handgun Sound FX Pack by Ovani Sound – a comprehensive collection of detailed, high-fidelity handgun handling foley with no gunfire sounds, ideal for realistic weapon systems and immersive first-person experiences.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With 361 total sounds, this pack includes everything from magazine handling and holstering to hammer clicks, dry triggers, and weapon pickups.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 76 9mm Pistol Sounds: Assembly, cocking, handling, dry trigger pulls, magazine inserts, table movement, and more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 55 Ammo and Brass Sounds: Bullet casing drops, box handling, and various ammo types including 9mm, .45 ACP, and .38 Special.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 99 Colt 1911 Pistol Sounds: Safety toggles, hammer movements, mag drops, table handling, rack slides, and loading sequences.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 62 Holstering Sounds: Draw and insert movements for leather, kydex, and zippered holsters across three weapon types.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 69 S&amp;amp;W Revolver Sounds: Cylinder actions, hammer cocks, trigger movements, reloading rounds, and detailed pickup/putdown foley.&lt;p&gt;Perfect for FPS games, military simulators, cinematic cutscenes, or any project where precise weapon handling is a must.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file is embedded with detailed metadata for rapid integration into your audio workflow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="weaponry_melee"&gt;&lt;a id="weaponry_melee" href="https://youtu.be/ge7F-Z3s2S4"&gt;Weaponry: Melee&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1081f701300ecd71bbc6ee188b50c0e6f9b9ac44.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=232961630d1eb74a0ff66039e19cd5ee"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing the Weaponry: Melee Sound FX Pack by Ovani Sound – a brutal and detailed arsenal of handcrafted audio for melee-based combat systems. Whether you're building a medieval brawler, post-apocalyptic survival game, or fantasy RPG, these sounds deliver the weight, grit, and satisfaction of up-close battle.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With 171 total sounds across blades, blunts, and polearms, this pack gives developers clean separation between weapon types and motion, supporting modular systems and animation layering.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 77 Blade Sounds: Large, medium, small, and thin strikes, parries, blocks, sheathing, and unsheathing – perfect for swords, daggers, or rapiers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 41 Blunt Sounds: Hard-hitting impacts and handling sounds for maces, hammers, and clubs of all sizes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 53 Polearm Sounds: Wooden haft-based swipes, pierces, and defensive maneuvers for spears, halberds, and staff weapons.&lt;p&gt;Designed with action-RPGs and fighting systems in mind, each sound is clear, cinematic, and ready for implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file is tagged with detailed metadata for fast implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="weaponry_ranged"&gt;&lt;a id="weaponry_ranged" href="https://youtu.be/GPUNZ6-48WU"&gt;Weaponry: Ranged&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d028310ba52c58935a705c028b94f091dfb0a874.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=bf851b3aa7c9695da217382ab80f7ee9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing the Weaponry: Ranged Sound FX Pack by Ovani Sound – an expertly curated library of projectile weapon sounds for stylized or historical combat systems. With rich, textured recordings that span gunpowder, bows, crossbows, and hand-thrown weapons, this pack gives your ranged attacks the bite they deserve.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Featuring 179 total sounds, you'll find immersive firing, reloading, and impact layers across a diverse arsenal, tailored for modular use in any shooter, RPG, or tactical game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 62 Firearm Sounds: Arquebuses, muskets, flintlock pistols, and cannons – with matching shots, reloads, and impacts that bring historical weapons to life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 84 Projectile Weapon Sounds: Includes longbows, crossbows, ballistae, slings, and small bows with layered draw, shot, and reload actions.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 33 Throwable Weapon Sounds: Arrows, spears, knives, shurikens, and stones with satisfying throw-and-impact sequences.&lt;p&gt;Ideal for games set in medieval, pirate, steampunk, or fantasy worlds, these sounds pair well with both stylized and realistic visuals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file includes detailed metadata for fast and accurate implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ntlanhlakutuvoiceoverpack"&gt;&lt;a id="ntlanhlakutuvoiceoverpack" href="https://youtu.be/efFavTnWU2o"&gt;Ntlanhla Kutu Voice Over Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8c936fb6fdbb1eebf6bf7bd364dc7546a59f6123.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=662e901e8640aa35b64eef6d0f57ac79"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0777/1491/5643/files/Ntlanhla_Kutu_Voice_Over_Pack.pdf"&gt;Click here to view the full list of voice lines in the Ntlanhla Kutu Voice Over Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Fully voice any character with the Ntlanhla Kutu Voice Over Pack by Ovani Sound. Featuring over 600 professionally recorded voice lines, this pack provides a versatile range of tones and expressions, perfect for giving life to an otherwise silent character! No AI used, 100% Human voice recordings.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Categories Included:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Accepting, Confirming, &amp;amp; Thanks – Kind, neutral, and rude variations for affirmation and gratitude.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Battle &amp;amp; Support Yells – Intense callouts and combat shouts for action-packed scenes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Commands – Tactical and situational instructions in far and near variations.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Declining &amp;amp; Confrontational – Polite refusals to strong dismissals for complex interactions.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;General Comments – Relatable phrases like “Gross” and “What now” to add personality.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Greetings &amp;amp; Farewells – Friendly and dismissive greetings and goodbyes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Puzzling – Lines for exploration and problem-solving scenarios.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Wordless Expressions – A large collection of attack grunts, laughs, gasps, sighs, and more.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This pack offers everything you need to create authentic, engaging characters that resonate with players.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;44.1kHz/16bit&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Each file is tagged with metadata to streamline your workflow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="godotmusicplugin"&gt;&lt;a id="godotmusicplugin"&gt;Godot Music Plugin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d9f6669ce8b51fc05d2b9da0f3596112d631d82d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=37b3cfb33eb3d51193e6becf51143fd8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Adding music to a game can be overwhelming. Our Unreal Music Plugin takes the headache out of the process and frees you to handle the more creative aspects of game development. You’ll see how you are able to easily trigger changes in song intensity, song selection, and random song play through our easy to use UI. All of this while working with seamless looping capability. _x000B_Pair this with one of our specially-made music packs, and you’re set up to make a captivating experience that players can get lost in.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unitymusicplugin"&gt;&lt;a id="unitymusicplugin"&gt;Unity Music Plugin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6144b36d437e8b41bd8fec26e2a2636dffdd1ca1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c7b309e3ae1fb0056dadcf42320ac92d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Adding music to a game can be overwhelming. Our Unity Music Plugin takes the headache out of the process and frees you to handle the more creative aspects of game development. _x000B_You’ll see how you are able to easily trigger changes in song intensity, song selection, and random song play through our easy to use UI. All of this while working with seamless looping capability. _x000B_Pair this with one of our specially-made music packs, and you’re set up to make a captivating experience that players can get lost in.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unrealmusicplugin"&gt;&lt;a id="unrealmusicplugin"&gt;Unreal Music Plugin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7cd10e87dbf472478296a7fd0460e31cf2bba181.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&am