emoved)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="2dcustomisablecharactersforunity"&gt;&lt;a id="2dcustomisablecharactersforunity"&gt;2D Customizable Characters for Unity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/41cb1f107932acdd5aab1d104f775e41832be0f3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=153854d8dfd306e4d0b5ec838aba2127"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;⚠️Note that this asset requires the UNITY Editor to run. Any exported spritesheets is normal PNG and can be used in any engines supporting spritesheet.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Finding high-resolution 2D characters in four directions can be a challenge. But an even bigger one is finding enough characters to populate your entire game! 2D Customizable Characters is a Unity solution specifically designed to solve this problem. This asset gives you two hand-painted and fully animated humanoid character models with in-depth customization options, allowing you to populate your game world with a wide variety of distinct and appealing characters.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="userinterfacesoundeffectsfantasycollection"&gt;&lt;a id="userinterfacesoundeffectsfantasycollection"&gt;User Interface Sound Effects Fantasy Collection&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1959e838cf78a361cf348147f28555340349a9ae.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1238ca8fdacf994d69da7694c94049ba"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This comprehensive, top-tier sound pack is a must-have for creating an enchanting, immersive, and user-friendly experience in any fantasy-themed game or application.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With over 420 meticulously crafted sounds, this collection includes everything you need to bring magic and life to your user interface.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="explosionsoundfxvolumeiiifantasy"&gt;&lt;a id="explosionsoundfxvolumeiiifantasy"&gt;Explosion Sound FX Volume III Fantasy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/93f23770d606a6fc7931c055d334add1d33e1a62.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e264f441eb67598244d09c75a72e9b42"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This magical sound pack is the definitive collection of fantasy-themed explosions— crafted to unleash arcane force, elemental chaos, and mystic destruction in any fantasy setting.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;From enchanted combustions to cursed detonations, each explosion delivers cinematic weight and magical impact, built to elevate spellcasting systems, magical combat, and boss encounters with fantasy flair.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="magicsoundeffectsalchemypack"&gt;&lt;a id="magicsoundeffectsalchemypack"&gt;Magic Sound Effects Alchemy Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9545cb2ad5a7fbaaed0b19c6f56f34d0228f6bdc.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e65b39851c696d22bb0f7fe52cbb5454"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into the world of the alchemist.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing: Magic Sound Effects - Alchemy Pack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dive into the magical craft of potion brewing with sounds for different stages of potion creation, including initiation, brewing, completion, failed experiments and more. With 150 expertly crafted sounds, this pack covers every step of the magical crafting process—from mixing mysterious ingredients to the final bubbling success (or failure) of your potion. Perfect for alchemists and crafting-focused gameplay.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
