iththreejs"&gt;3D Data Masterclass: Build Data-Driven Web Apps with THREE.js&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#augmentedrealitymasterclass_buildarwebappswitharjs"&gt;Augmented Reality Masterclass: Build AR Web Apps with AR.js&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#aistudiono-codemagic_generateappswithoutwritingcode"&gt;AI Studio No-Code Magic: Generate Apps Without Writing Code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#3dwebgamelegends_buildbabylonjsgameslikeapro"&gt;3D Web Game Legends: Build Babylon.js Games Like a Pro&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#codefoundations_mastercommandprompthtmlandcssfromscratch"&gt;Code Foundations: Master Command Prompt, HTML and CSS from Scratch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="micro-frontendfoundations_thefutureofscalablewebapps"&gt;&lt;a id="micro-frontendfoundations_thefutureofscalablewebapps"&gt;Micro-Frontend Foundations: The Future of Scalable Web Apps&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/305b4737dab02c2cae85ed7bc7cc930789d7a8f8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=fd6574f7b6e1f62a656eb00c9ec55c4a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;As frontend applications grow, so do the challenges of scale, independence, and maintainability.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course introduces you to the core concepts of micro-frontends—a modern architectural pattern for splitting frontend apps into smaller, autonomous pieces that can evolve independently.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Understand what micro-frontends are, why they matter, and when to use them&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Explore strategies for routing, communication, and code sharing across micro-apps&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Learn integration methods using tools like Module Federation, iframes, or custom loaders&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Discover team-based scaling, deployment flexibility, and performance trade-offs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're preparing to scale a frontend system or exploring future-proof patterns, this course helps you think beyond monoliths and build with modularity in mind.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes lifetime access. Scalable thinking. Real-world structure.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to explore the architecture powering modern teams and large apps—this is your starting point.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="micro-frontendmastery_advancedarchitectureforscalableapps"&gt;&lt;a id="micro-frontendmastery_advancedarchitectureforscalableapps"&gt;Micro-Frontend Mastery: Advanced Architecture for Scalable Apps&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7f81e476ff9cec258ed678d645ded4608ff92c2f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e027917be04ebb5ef4ba104c93d9d963"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Scaling frontend development isn’t just about more code—it’s about smarter architecture.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course dives deep into advanced micro-frontend patterns, showing you how to structure, coordinate, and deploy independently-managed frontend modules at scale—without sacrificing performance or developer velocity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Explore advanced integration strategies like Module Federation, Web Components, and dynamic loading&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Learn how to manage cross-app communication, shared state, and dependency boundaries&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Design deployment workflows for independent teams and isolated builds&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Navigate real-world challenges: performance bottlenecks, versioning, and UI consistency&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're leading a large frontend team or transitioning to a modular architecture, this course helps you understand how to build scalable systems that stay maintainable as they grow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes lifetime access. Real patterns. Real challenges. Real solutions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to move from theory to implementation—this is your deep dive into modern frontend architecture.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="javascriptwebdeployment_fromcodetoproductionwithconfidence"&gt;&lt;a id="javascriptwebdeployment_fromcodetoproductionwithconfidence"&gt;JavaScript Web Deployment: From Code to Production with Confidence&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/19bc6463bcf672b84ecc29044d90cb6f125b022f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2b2aaa65b4814be67b77882d6f1da717"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Writing JavaScript is only half the journey—getting it live is where things get real.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course focuses on the deployment process: the tools, environments, and decisions that take your web apps from your local machine to a production-ready state users can access anywhere.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Learn how to prepare, build, and optimize JavaScript apps for real-world hosting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Understand environments, static vs. dynamic deployment, and build tools like Webpack or Vite&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Explore hosting platforms, version control workflows, and CI/CD basics&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Get hands-on with common services like GitHub Pages, Vercel, Netlify, or custom servers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're deploying a personal project, client app, or learning to ship professionally, this course gives you the confidence to publish and manage modern JavaScript applications.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes lifetime access. From local dev to global reach.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to stop coding in isolation and start shipping with purpose—this is your next step.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="reactdatapro_buildchartjsappsthatimpress"&gt;&lt;a id="reactdatapro_buildchartjsappsthatimpress"&gt;React Data Pro: Build Chart.js Apps That Impress&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/60f9d0be743e5d2bfb233bd7bb72fafe0d47e95d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2e26e119f5e17235b16519e4af8f1f24"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Data is only useful when it's clear—and great visualizations bring it to life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course shows you how to integrate Chart.js into modern React applications, helping you create interactive, responsive, and meaningful visual displays that users can understand at a glance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Learn how to connect React components with Chart.js and manage data flow&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Explore chart types like bar, line, pie, and dynamic updates using props and state&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Understand customization, layout control, and visual theming for real-world use&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Get comfortable structuring data, handling API responses, and displaying trends clearly&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're building dashboards, reports, or product interfaces, this course helps you present data with purpose—and build visualizations that are more than just pretty.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes lifetime access. Communicate clearly. Build with confidence.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to turn raw numbers into usable insight—this is your toolkit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="fullstackmasterclass_builddynamicappswithejs"&gt;&lt;a id="fullstackmasterclass_builddynamicappswithejs"&gt;Fullstack Masterclass: Build Dynamic Apps with EJS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/94e5d5b393b7e4e704b699489487caadc65605d2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=af12508b1f35d84e66c2569c9ceba217"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fullstack development doesn’t always require complex frameworks—sometimes, simplicity is the best place to start.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course explores how to build dynamic, server-rendered web applications using EJS, giving you full control over the backend logic and frontend output in a clean, efficient way.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Learn how to use EJS to render dynamic content with variables, loops, and conditionals&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Connect server-side logic (like Node.js and Express) to templated frontends&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Understand routing, request handling, and form submission in fullstack apps&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Explore the structure of MVC-style applications and how to keep code maintainable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're building your first fullstack project or learning how server-side rendering works under the hood, this course gives you the tools to create clean, responsive, and dynamic web apps with clarity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes lifetime access. Simpler stack. Real-world results.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to learn how front and back work together—this is your fullstack starting point.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="fullstackwebmastery_buildappswithmongodb"&gt;&lt;a id="fullstackwebmastery_buildappswithmongodb"&gt;Fullstack Web Mastery: Build Apps with MongoDB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/465b700d61119d814c3dd410ba135aa5774b4e47.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c98c8bff8371318aeadd0d2b25215667"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Modern web apps don’t just live in the browser—they run on a solid, scalable data foundation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course explores how to build fullstack applications using MongoDB as your database layer, connecting backend logic with frontend interfaces through a practical, developer-friendly approach.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Learn how to structure, query, and update data using MongoDB and Mongoose&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Understand how to connect a Node.js/Express backend to a MongoDB database&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Explore fullstack flows: from data models and API routes to frontend integration&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Work with key concepts like schemas, validation, CRUD operations, and RESTful design&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're building personal projects, MVPs, or learning how modern stacks fit together, this course helps you gain confidence working across the full web development stack—with data at the center.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes lifetime access. Data-driven. Fullstack-ready.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to connect your frontend to a real database and think like a fullstack dev—this is your next step.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="backendbrilliance_restapisnodeexpressandmongomadeeasy"&gt;&lt;a id="backendbrilliance_restapisnodeexpressandmongomadeeasy"&gt;Backend Brilliance: REST APIs, Node, Express and Mongo Made Easy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/84b2fc56bd241412f0e03e9fce3530971e40523f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e7385b4784d5df23916fc25ea36a8c86"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A solid backend is the engine behind every responsive, data-driven web app.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course breaks down the essentials of backend development using Node.js, Express, and MongoDB, showing you how to create and connect RESTful APIs that power modern applications.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Learn how to set up servers, handle routes, and manage middleware with Express&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Build and structure RESTful APIs for clean communication between front and back&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Connect to MongoDB using Mongoose, and perform common database operations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Understand the flow of data from client requests to stored records and back again&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you’re new to backend logic or strengthening your fullstack skills, this course gives you the tools to write server code that’s readable, scalable, and production-aware.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes lifetime access. Clean structure. Clear logic.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to go beyond the frontend and understand how the web really works—this is your foundation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="nodejsbootcamp_thecompletebackendmasterypath"&gt;&lt;a id="nodejsbootcamp_thecompletebackendmasterypath"&gt;Node.js Bootcamp: The Complete Backend Mastery Path&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&g